com.ge.dspmicro.machinegateway.api.adapter

Interface ISubscriptionAdapterListener


  • public interface ISubscriptionAdapterListener
    Services that are interested in subscription for which data is supplied by ISubscriptionAdapter instances can provide and implementation of this interface to subscription Adapters. Ideally, the should add themselves to every adapter so they can be notified in case a subscription they are interested in becomes available in an adapter at a later stage that was not supplying it at the first.
    Since:
    16.2
